html:
bool redistributeManuallyAssignedLicences

Whether to recalculate manually granted licenses. By default, "false."

Available values

true

All licenses are recalculated, including overriding manually granted licenses based on role priority. Use when a full license recalculation is required.

false

Manually granted licenses remain unchanged. Recommended for most scenarios to preserve administrator adjustments.
